high_descs: Go across to the coffeetable beside the microwave.
Pick up the butterknife on the counter.
Go past the fridge to the table, turn left, then turn left into the room, and go to the bed.
Slice the apple on the bed.
Place the butterknife on the third shelf in the middle.
Pick up the slice of apple closer to the front.
Turn right at the door, then turn right and go past the fridge to the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat the apple, and pick the apple back up.
Turn to the coffeetable beside the microwave.
Place the apple slice on the coffeetable in the back to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple slice on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Walk straight and reach the coffeetable on the left side in which oven is placed.
Take a butterknife from the table which is next to oven.
Turn left and walk straight and turn left to and enter into the bedroom after crossing the mini apple table. Then reach the bed.
Cut a green apple in to pieces which is kept on the bed.
Then put the butterknife on the left side shelf.
Take a piece of apple from the bed.
Turn back and walk out of the room. Turn right and again take a right to reach the microwave.
Open the oven and put the apple piece inside the oven and close the door. After few seconds, open the oven and take the apple out and then close the oven.
Move little bit towards of the coffeetable
Put the apple piece on the left top corner of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple piece on the left top corner of the CoffeeTable

high_descs: walk to the coffeetable with the knife on top of it.
Pick up the butterknife from the countertop.
walk to the bedroom with the apple.
Cut the apple on the bed.
Put the butterknife away on the shelves.
pick up a piece of apple from the bed.
turn around and go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, heat the apple up and then remove the apple.
Open the coffeetable and put the spatula in it.
Turn and put the apple on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Get a knife, cut the apple on the CoffeeTable to take to the kitchen.
